 # what is twilio message automation?
# Twilio message automation refers to the use of Twilio's messaging services to automate the sending and receiving of messages.
#  This can include SMS, MMS, and even WhatsApp messages. 
# With Twilio's APIs, businesses can set up automated workflows to send notifications, reminders, alerts, and promotional messages to customers without manual intervention.
#  This automation can be triggered by various events such as user actions, scheduled times, or specific conditions being met.
#  It helps businesses improve communication efficiency and enhance customer engagement.